lead_paragraph: Saudi billionaire Prince Alwaleed bin Talal has called Donald Trump a disgrace to the United States following his call for a ban on Muslims entering the country, and demanded the Republican front-runner withdraw from the U.S. presidential race.

headline.main: Saudi Prince Alwaleed Calls Trump a Disgrace
